56:15.980 --> 56:17.160
intelligence gathering systems

56:17.160 --> 56:18.720
to monitor both

56:18.720 --> 56:19.960
non-human craft

56:19.960 --> 56:21.820
and alien reproduction vehicles.

56:22.380 --> 56:23.000
There are plenty

56:23.000 --> 56:23.980
of interesting cases,

56:24.120 --> 56:24.400
including

56:24.400 --> 56:26.880
slowly rotating triangles

56:26.880 --> 56:27.860
over Indo-PATCOM,

56:27.940 --> 56:28.800
Indo-Pacific Command.

56:28.800 --> 56:30.360
And within Matthew Brown's

56:30.360 --> 56:31.820
Immaculate Constellation document,

56:32.520 --> 56:33.760
saucer-shaped craft

56:33.760 --> 56:34.420
seemingly using

56:34.420 --> 56:35.900
cloud coverage

56:35.900 --> 56:37.120
as cover and all that.

56:37.920 --> 56:38.040
So,

56:38.420 --> 56:38.880
but the connection

56:38.880 --> 56:39.420
I'm trying to make

56:39.420 --> 56:39.840
and why I think

56:39.840 --> 56:40.500
a strong argument

56:40.500 --> 56:41.780
Tom DeLonge was exposed

56:41.780 --> 56:43.260
to Immaculate Constellation

56:43.260 --> 56:43.880
in 2017,

56:44.160 --> 56:44.580
the year

56:44.580 --> 56:45.260
IMCON

56:45.260 --> 56:46.300
began,

56:46.600 --> 56:46.700
is

56:46.700 --> 56:48.060
