56:48.060 --> 56:49.140
to that Joe Rogan interview,

56:50.340 --> 56:51.260
Tom DeLonge talks about

56:51.260 --> 56:52.420
episodic visits

56:52.420 --> 56:53.420
of craft.

56:54.180 --> 56:54.720
He says that

56:54.720 --> 56:55.760
his high-level

56:55.760 --> 56:56.540
sources

56:56.540 --> 56:58.280
in the NRO

56:58.280 --> 56:59.000
specifically

56:59.000 --> 57:00.060
told him

57:00.060 --> 57:00.780
that scientists

57:00.780 --> 57:01.500
and eggheads

57:01.500 --> 57:02.260
had figured out

57:02.260 --> 57:02.880
ways to

57:02.880 --> 57:04.060
basically pre-predict

57:04.060 --> 57:04.880
when and where

57:04.880 --> 57:06.320
craft would appear

57:06.320 --> 57:07.220
and thus

57:07.220 --> 57:08.320
satellites

57:08.320 --> 57:09.080
and imagery

57:09.080 --> 57:10.060
intelligence platforms

57:10.060 --> 57:11.080
would capture

57:11.080 --> 57:11.900
these quote-unquote

57:11.900 --> 57:12.940
episodic visits.

57:13.620 --> 57:14.120
His connections

57:14.120 --> 57:14.780
to the NRO,

57:15.200 --> 57:16.280
whilst he was at

57:16.280 --> 57:17.060
TTSA,

57:17.460 --> 57:18.120
Lou Elizondo

57:18.120 --> 57:19.260
was liaison

57:19.260 --> 57:20.220
to the NRO.

57:20.380 --> 57:21.500
He was liaison

57:21.500 --> 57:22.140
to the NRO.

57:22.600 --> 57:22.840
Whoa,

57:23.040 --> 57:23.460
I don't think

57:23.460 --> 57:23.900
a lot of people

57:23.900 --> 57:24.400
know that.

57:24.400 --> 57:26.780
That's not public

57:26.780 --> 57:27.120
knowledge,

57:27.220 --> 57:27.420
but yeah,

57:27.460 --> 57:28.000
he was liaison

57:28.000 --> 57:28.700
to the NRO.

57:28.860 --> 57:29.420
How'd you figure

57:29.420 --> 57:29.880
that out?

57:30.360 --> 57:30.840
Curriculum,

57:31.100 --> 57:32.620
CV.

57:32.900 --> 57:33.220
Okay.

57:33.860 --> 57:34.220
CV.

57:34.480 --> 57:34.760
Okay.

57:34.760 --> 57:35.540
Liaison to the NRO.

57:35.740 --> 57:36.300
And if you look

57:36.300 --> 57:36.820
at the Immaculate

57:36.820 --> 57:37.880
Constellation documents,

57:38.140 --> 57:39.420
numerous sightings

57:39.420 --> 57:40.060
talk about how

57:40.060 --> 57:41.100
the sensor collection

57:41.100 --> 57:42.020
platform seemingly

57:42.020 --> 57:44.640
