57:52.360 --> 57:52.980
It had foreknowledge.

57:52.980 --> 57:53.880
It could track

57:53.880 --> 57:54.500
the erratically

57:54.500 --> 57:55.220
moving tic-tac

57:55.220 --> 57:55.880
or the saucer.

57:56.480 --> 57:57.780
So I think

57:57.780 --> 57:58.280
there's a connection

57:58.280 --> 57:58.840
there with those

57:58.840 --> 57:59.620
episodic visits

57:59.620 --> 58:00.700
and the foreknowledge

58:00.700 --> 58:01.740
