58:01.740 --> 58:02.300
in the Immaculate

58:02.300 --> 58:03.240
Constellation documents.

58:03.340 --> 58:03.800
The timelines

58:03.800 --> 58:04.340
add up too.

58:04.740 --> 58:05.480
I think that's

58:05.480 --> 58:06.840
