58:12.860 --> 58:13.860
But I think

58:13.860 --> 58:14.440
there's some

58:14.440 --> 58:15.140
interesting questions

58:15.140 --> 58:15.600
there that could

58:15.600 --> 58:16.060
be explored.

58:16.500 --> 58:17.260
That's so fascinating.

58:17.400 --> 58:18.260
I think the more

58:18.260 --> 58:19.780
you read books

58:19.780 --> 58:21.360
