58:40.540 --> 58:40.940
Yeah, based on

58:40.940 --> 58:41.640
the Jason Committee.

58:41.880 --> 58:42.740
The Jason Committee

58:42.740 --> 58:43.480
or it was like,

58:43.540 --> 58:44.160
I think it was like

58:44.160 --> 58:44.880
this international

58:44.880 --> 58:46.020
